{
  "stem": "26609.9",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But Jews gathered there together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was a market.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there were little synagogues.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And not far from there that was [INAUDIBLE] And you called it [INAUDIBLE] It was a big part there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there were, because there lived only Jews, the Germans established the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They fenced it around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a huge place, fenced around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And before you get-- and a gate to go in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Before you went there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the street, what was still [INAUDIBLE] On one side of the street, there was a [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fenced onto-- the same like this, but before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the Germans had their buildings there, the Gestapo, with the door open.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And as we went down-- so we went down together, my, myself with my child, my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know where her husband-- he didn't go with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Maybe he went later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I don't remember seeing him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Could be that he went a little later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And my younger sister, who survived, and lived in France now, whom I found 22 years after the war, I didn't know that she's alive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I just traveled from here to New York, to United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That's another story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I'll say later about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Though she was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we had to go-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a big group of people [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And pass near on the right hand side, before going to-- on the way to the ghetto, we had to pass that buildings-- those buildings with the Germans, with the door open.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they looked through as we went in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They didn't want old people at the ghetto, only younger people, because later they took them out for work.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
